# Email Configuration for No Food Waste Admin Portal
# 
# IMPORTANT: For Gmail accounts, you MUST use an App Password, not your regular password!
#
# Steps to set up Gmail App Password:
# 1. Enable 2-factor authentication on your Gmail account
# 2. Go to Google Account settings > Security > App passwords
# 3. Generate a new App password for "Mail"
# 4. Use that 16-character password below (remove spaces)
#
# Example configuration:

EMAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
EMAIL_PORT=587
EMAIL_ADDRESS=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-16-character-app-password

# For other email providers:
# - Outlook/Hotmail: EMAIL_HOST=smtp-mail.outlook.com, EMAIL_PORT=587
# - Yahoo: EMAIL_HOST=smtp.mail.yahoo.com, EMAIL_PORT=587
# - Custom SMTP: Check with your email provider for SMTP settings
